file.name: TelemetryFeatures.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
TelemetryFeatures:
  type: object
  description: Telemetry Features
  properties:
    decisioningMethod:
      $ref: "./DecisioningMethod.yaml#/DecisioningMethod"
      description: Decisioning Method used
    executeMboxCount:
      type: integer
      description: Number of mboxes in execute request
    executePageLoad:
      type: boolean
      description: Indicates if execute pageLoad was used
    prefetchMboxCount:
      type: integer
      description: Number of prefetched mboxes
    prefetchPageLoad:
      type: boolean
      description: Indicates if prefetch pageLoad was used
    prefetchViewCount:
      type: integer
      description: Number of prefetched views
